Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.30,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte mi, hneď som späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.28,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dobre, počkám.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:16.25,Rena,,0,0,0,,Dobrý večer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.34,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,R-Rena...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.92,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo tu robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.80,Rena,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun, už si večeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:25.36,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:28.01,Rena,,0,0,0,,Výborne!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:30.20,Rena,,0,0,0,,Niečo som ti priniesla.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:33.12,Rena,,0,0,0,,Môžem to u vás v kuchyni prihriať a -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:38.27,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Vďaka, ale my budeme za chvíľu jesť.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.00,Rena,,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:44.29,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Moja mama vždy navarí veľa jedla.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:45.73,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Takže -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:48.91,Rena,,0,0,0,,Tvoja mama naozaj uvarila večeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:53.12,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,No, totiž... Práve teraz ju varí...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.51,Rena,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:59.20,Rena,,0,0,0,,Prečo ma klameš? Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.11,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ja neklamem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.34,Rena,,0,0,0,,KLAMEŠ!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:05.42,Rena,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun bude mať na večeru polievku v prášku, mám pravdu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.85,Rena,,0,0,0,,Bravčovú s trochou zázvoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.93,Rena,,0,0,0,,A kúpil si ju v Seventh Market-e.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:12.68,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ako ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:15.52,Rena,,0,0,0,,Ale to ti nestačí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.80,Rena,,0,0,0,,Mal by si jesť aj zeleninu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.39,Rena,,0,0,0,,Tak už konečne otvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:23.78,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:27.59,Rena,,0,0,0,,No tak, Keiichi. Otvor dvere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:30.03,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prosím ťa, choď preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.04,Rena,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.37,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Odíď...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.42,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,VYPADNI!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:39.15,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:39.84,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Zmizni!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.40,Rena,,0,0,0,,Prestaň Keiichi! To bolí!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:42.65,Rena,,0,0,0,,Bolí to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:42.65,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:46.66,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč! Choď preč! Choď už preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.45,Rena,,0,0,0,,To naozaj bolí!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.22,Rena,,0,0,0,,Mrzí ma ak som s tým žartom zašla priďaleko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:52.04,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč! Choď preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:51.81,Rena,,0,0,0,,Prepáč mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.47,Rena,,0,0,0,,Prepáč ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.35,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.60,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.90,Rena,,0,0,0,,Prepáč! Prepáč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:58.85,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:03:59.69,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.23,Rena,,0,0,0,,Prepáč mi to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:00.90,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Choď preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:01.61,Rena,,0,0,0,,Prepáč mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.36,Rena,,0,0,0,,Prepáč...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.83,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Oishi, ste tam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.46,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Bola tu Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.42,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prišla na návštevu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:21.98,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:26.72,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Oishi, mohli by ste mi povedať čo všetko viete o Rene?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:30.93,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Môžem ale sľúb mi že to nepovieš nikomu inému.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:36.98,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A pamätaj že je to z časti čistá špekulácia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.73,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.77,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tak dobre.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.47,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pravdu povediac, je mi to trochu podozrivé.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.69,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Podozrievate Renu a ostatných?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:49.07,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tak som to nemyslel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.57,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mám namysli Oyashira.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.58,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Či už je Oyashirova kliatba skutočná alebo nie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.92,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}vieš...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.13,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pamätáš si na tú udalosť o ktorej som ti hovoril?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:11.52,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Myslíte to ako porozbíjala okná po celej škole?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:12.22,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Áno.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:14.83,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boli pri tom zranený traja chlapci.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:21.81,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Troch svojich blízkych priateľov takmer prizabila baseballovou pálkou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.75,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Pálkou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:29.95,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aké keďže ani škola ani zranený nepodali žalobu, už sa to ďalej nevyšetrovalo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:35.08,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Z neznámych dôvodov každý z nich odmietol vypovedať.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:41.21,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeden z nich dokonca odmietol výpoveď aj napriek tomu že mu po tom ostalo trvalé poranenie oka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:44.08,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Odmietol vypovedať aj podať žalobu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.21,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haló?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:51.72,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maebara-kun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:52.91,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Počuješ ma?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.80,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo to ... hovorí... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.06,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo sa deje, Maebara-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.23,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,"Prepáč... mi..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.69,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maebara-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:05.90,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maebara-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:05.90,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,"Prepáč mi."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.32,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haló!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.36,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,"Prepáč mi..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.45,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.49,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.61,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Netušila som že máš tak rád baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.23,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Rozptyľuješ ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.63,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nechaj ma tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.76,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Prestaň mávať s tou vecou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.51,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.92,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Povedala som aby si prestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.70,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prestal som.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:40.62,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Myslím tým ... už to nikdy viac nerob!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.57,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:45.69,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nemyslím že by som tým niekomu škodil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:47.97,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:50.67,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Áno? A komu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.20,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,To nieje tvoja pálka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:57.32,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Zabudol tu žiak ktorý sa odišiel z dediny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.53,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ale je to zvláštne...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.75,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Brat sa odsťahoval a sestra zostala tu, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.64,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ty to vieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:09.99,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Satoshi Hojo. Satokin brat, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.09,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Minulí rok bol "unesený obrom" a zmizol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.84,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Počul som že aj on trénoval s pálkou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.51,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Tesne pred tým ako zmizol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:23.14,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Je to niečo ako znamenie tých ktorý majú byť zasiahnutý Oyashirovou kliatbou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:27.31,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale aj tak! Všetkých si vystrašil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.88,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ak to má byť nejaký hlúpy vtip,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.00,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,tak prestaň napodobňovať Satoshiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:37.79,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Tak ma počúvaj! Ja neviem NIČ o Satoshim,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.21,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,pretože to predo mnou stále tajíte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.41,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nesnažíme sa to pred tebou tajiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.87,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,A takisto ste ma vôbec nechceli vystrašiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:47.61,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Tak prečo predo mnou stále niečo skrývate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.88,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Tak sme to nechceli ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:53.20,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Pýtal som sa ťa či sa na stavenisku niečo stalo zvláštne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.45,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Povedala si mi že sa tam nestalo nič!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.43,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Aj napriek tomu že tam našli rozsekanú mŕtvolu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.22,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Si odporná klamárka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:02.51,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Je mi to ľúto... ale to nebola skutočná lož...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:07.42,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Priatelia nemajú medzi sebou tajomstvá, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.40,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Preto vy nieste moji priatelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.27,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,K-Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.23,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:19.07,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,A to "ohagi" čo si mi priniesla bolo výborné.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:21.41,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Tak dobré až mi z neho ústa krvácali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.74,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ktorá z vás to spravila?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.00,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.31,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Alebo Rena?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:30.88,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Bez boja ma nedostanete!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.92,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nemyslite si že sa ma zbavíte tak ako ste sa zbavili Satoshiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:42.47,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Mimochodom, počul som tiež že si sa pár krát pobila z predákom stavby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.52,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Myslela si si že to všetko utajíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.81,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ako si to zistil?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:53.67,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Zvoní.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.86,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Mali by sme ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.32,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Si strašne zlý, Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:03.70,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Už viem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:09.21,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Takže {\i1}ten{\i0} hajzeľ ti to povedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:14.97,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mala som ho zabiť keď som mala šancu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:20.75,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Asi už zabudol že som ho nechala ísť len preto že ide tento rok do dôchodku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:23.52,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Do šľaka! Do šľaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.92,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Tá sviňa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.10,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Zabijem ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:32.35,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Aký hajzeľ? Myslíš Oishiho?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.88,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Načo je jej tá sekera?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.68,Rena,,0,0,0,,Našla som ťa, Keiichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.74,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo odo mňa chceš?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.41,Rena,,0,0,0,,Chodíme domov tou istou cestou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.89,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,A načo je ti tá sekera?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.11,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:24.59,Rena,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun, teba niečo trápi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.45,Rena,,0,0,0,,Vidím že si vystrašený.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.48,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nie som.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:35.47,Rena,,0,0,0,,Bolo mi ľúto keď Satoshi "odišiel".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:40.40,Rena,,0,0,0,,Rozmýšľala som čo by sa zmenilo keby som sa ho pokúsila varovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.31,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,"Odišiel"? Tým myslíš že ho uniesol obor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.30,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.04,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ktorá z vás ho odstránila?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:49.94,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.91,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Mion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.75,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Alebo niekto iný z dediny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:53.85,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Odpovedz mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:57.65,Rena,,0,0,0,,Ja neviem o čom hovoríš.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.70,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Poviem ti o čom hovorím!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.28,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Chcem vedieť kto spôsobil všetky tie úmrtia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.20,Rena,,0,0,0,,Mýliš sa, Keiichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.95,Rena,,0,0,0,,Za to nemôže žiadny {\i1}človek{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.79,Rena,,0,0,0,,Rozhodol o tom Oyashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.88,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Oyashirova kliatba je len obyčajná povera!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:22.17,Rena,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun, ty neveríš v Oyashira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:25.34,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Samozrejme že nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:27.39,Rena,,0,0,0,,Oyashiro existuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:31.96,Rena,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun, poznal si už niekoho kto sa ti neustále len ospravedlňoval?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.94,Rena,,0,0,0,,Celý čas...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:41.30,Rena,,0,0,0,,Oyashiro prišiel za mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:45.28,Rena,,0,0,0,,Preto som najprv odišla a potom som sa zasa vrátila.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:49.28,Rena,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun, ja jediná ti môžem pomôcť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.83,Rena,,0,0,0,,Nenechám ťa "odísť."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:55.21,Rena,,0,0,0,,Tak mi o tom povedz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.16,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,O čom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.09,Rena,,0,0,0,,Rena si ťa vypočuje...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:03.05,Rena,,0,0,0,,Pomôže ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.05,Rena,,0,0,0,,Tak jej o tom povedz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.91,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo chcete?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.13,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo odo mňa chcete?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:48.63,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ďalšia rana pôjde do vašich ksichtov, vy svine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:59.00,SText1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\c&HFFFFFF&}Higurashi no Naku Koro Ni
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:04.01,SText2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\i1}Pretože to že som paranoidný\Nešte neznamená, že po mne nejdú...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.49,Rena,,0,0,0,,Mal by si ostať ležať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:11.62,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Rena...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:14.77,Rena,,0,0,0,,Za chvíľu príde doktor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.31,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo tu robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.71,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Už som tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.25,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Mion? Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:25.41,Rena,,0,0,0,,Tvoji rodičia nie sú doma, tak som zavolala ju.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.41,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Hej! Vyzeráš v poriadku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.36,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nezdá sa že by si potreboval pomoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.52,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rena, zavolala si kouča?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:38.92,Rena,,0,0,0,,Volala som mu hneď po tom ako som volala tebe. Povedal že hneď príde.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:44.71,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fs40.5\bord0\shad0\pos(954,60.75)}Slovom\h“kouč”\h(pôvodne\hanglické\hslovo\h"coach")\hsa\hbežne\hoslovuje\hbaseballový\htréner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.19,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Akého "kouča" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.98,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan, ty ho nepoznáš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:47.25,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Keď hovorím "kouč", myslím tým TOHO kouča.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.90,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nedávno si začal hrať baseball, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:53.65,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kouč bude určite rád.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.94,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Takže kto je ten "kouč" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.00,Rena,,0,0,0,,Kouč je proste kouč.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.50,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ale KTO je to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.05,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo je vám?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.41,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Už viem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.28,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kým kouč príde, spravíme si trestné kolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.50,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Trestné kolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:19.18,Rena,,0,0,0,,Zabudol si na svoju domácu úlohu s "ohagi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:21.20,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\pos(954,65.25)}Ohagi sú ryžové guličky plnené ihlou z minulého dielu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.29,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo to robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.57,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nehýb sa. Je to trestné kolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:33.03,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo to má znamenať?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.45,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo s tým chceš robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:37.91,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan, to už by si mohol vedieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:41.46,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo? Čo by som mal vedieť?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:49.60,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Predpokladali sme že bol pod vplyvom drogy ale testy to nepotvrdili.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.13,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,No tak, vzdaj to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:58.56,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.99,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,PRESTAŇ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.80,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Sú tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:51.07,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rena a Mion patrili k ľuďom zodpovedným za tie vraždy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.96,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okrem nich boli do toho zapojený aj štyria alebo piati dospelí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.53,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Používajú bielu dodávku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:59.23,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomitakeova smrť bola spôsobená nejakou drogou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.91,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ako dôkaz prikladám striekačku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.22,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.06,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prečo sa to muselo skončiť takto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.03,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Tam je!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:34.96,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Zadné dvere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.54,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Vydržte, prosím.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.58,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san! Máte hovor na vonkajšej linke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.42,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Vďaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:52.25,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Je to hovor z telefónnej búdky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.30,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Tu Oishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.01,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O-Oishi-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.38,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.29,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Stalo sa niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:07.60,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Čo je ti?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.21,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fr18\fs90\shad0\bord0\c&HA5A5A5&\pos(1062,243)}Telefónna búdka
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.21,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fr18\fs90\shad0\bord0\c&HA5A5A5&\pos(1161,535.5)}v Hinamizawe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.52,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ja... ja...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.18,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Upokoj sa, Maebara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.61,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Posielam za tebou dôstojníka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.56,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,A aj ja hneď prídem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:23.03,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To... to už nepomôže.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.36,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fr8\fs90\shad0\bord0\pos(909,144)\c&HA5A5A5&}V Hinamizawe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.36,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fr8\fs78.75\shad0\bord0\c&HA5A5A5&\pos(963,342)}je len jedna búdka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.36,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fr8\fs81\shad0\bord0\c&HA5A5A5&\pos(993,517.5)}Poslal som hliadku,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.36,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fr8\fs90\shad0\bord0\c&HA5A5A5&\pos(1029,695.25)}budú tam za
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.36,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fr8\fs90\shad0\bord0\c&HA5A5A5&\pos(960,861.75)}5 minút.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.45,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Hlavne sa upokoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.70,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Povedz mi, čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.12,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,To bude trvať pridlho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.31,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Koľko chlapov má hliadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:33.96,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Dvaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.06,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Zavolali ste dôstojníka ktorý to tam má na starosť?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.22,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Má práve pochôdzku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.64,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Kuma-chan! Nachystajte auto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:43.68,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Áno, pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.47,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Haló, Maebara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.52,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Dôstojník je už na ceste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.37,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Príde za dve-tri minúty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:54.29,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Meabara-san, kto to spravil? Koľko ich bolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:18:00.30,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Myslel som si... že za to môžu ľudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.60,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ale teraz si myslím...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:09.94,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Teraz {\i0}viem{\i1} že Oyashiro existuje!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.96,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.25,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Stál rovno za mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:22.56,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Bežal som stále ďalej a ďalej ale on sa ma držal ako tieň.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:28.18,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,A kúsok po kúsku bol stále bližšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:35.10,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san? Práve teraz... je tam... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.83,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je tu.. Je rovno za mnou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.36,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kto je tam?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.57,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem sa otočiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:48.97,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Bojím sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:53.32,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Ja viem že sa bojíš, ale ja to musím vedieť!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.55,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Len sa trocha obzri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:19:00.00,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san! Kto je tam? Kto stojí za tebou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:06.30,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san, neškriabeš si vlastné hrdlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.55,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Že nie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.38,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haló! Maebara-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.17,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maebara-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.90,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Odpu...stite... mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.48,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san! Auto je pripravené!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:22.49,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.78,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,"Odpustite mi?"...
